e=&gt;end: 结束框
st-&gt;op-&gt;cond
cond(yes)-&gt;io-&gt;e
cond(no)-&gt;sub1(right)-&gt;op
</code></pre>
<pre><code class="language-flow">st=&gt;start: 开始框
op=&gt;operation: 处理框
cond=&gt;condition: 判断框(是或否?)
